  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1111">
<l>naṉṉīrai vāḻi yaṉiccamē niṉṉiṉum </l>
<l>meṉṉīraḷ yāmvīḻ pavaḷ</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>May you flourish, O Anicham! you have a delicate nature. But my beloved is more delicate than you.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
